<teaserText grammarName="coremedia-richtext-1.0"><div xmlns="http://www.coremedia.com/2003/richtext-1.0" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><p>Warm up with delicious fall comfort food. Keep warm with hearty dishes that satisfy appetites and comfort food cravings.</p></div></teaserText>
<detailText grammarName="coremedia-richtext-1.0"><div xmlns="http://www.coremedia.com/2003/richtext-1.0" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><p class="p--heading-3">Warm up with delicious fall comfort food</p><p>Keep warm with <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Navigation/Microsites/05_Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Fall%20Recipes%20Page.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Navigation/Microsites/05_Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Fall%20Recipes%20Page">hearty dishes</a> that satisfy appetites and comfort food cravings. Savor the flavors of fall with cozy dinner <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Navigation/Microsites/05_Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Fall%20Recipes%20Page.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Navigation/Microsites/05_Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Fall%20Recipes%20Page">recipes</a>, warm <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Baking%20Pans/Baking%20Pans%20External%20Category%20Page.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Baking%20Pans/Baking%20Pans%20External%20Category%20Page">casseroles</a>, and simmering soups. Rich in flavor, the most satisfying fall menus feature in-season ingredients in comforting combinations for cool-weather meals.</p><p class="p--heading-3">Seasonal fruits and vegetables</p><p>Using fresh produce that is abundant in the fall is not only the best tasting, but is also a sensory pleasure that can truly enhance the cooking experience. Autumn's bumper crop of fruits and vegetables offer a range of intense flavors and substantial textures.<br/></p><p>Root vegetables and <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Videos/How-To/How%20to%20prep%20butternut%20squash%20Vimeo%20Video.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Videos/How-To/How%20to%20prep%20butternut%20squash%20Vimeo%20Video">winter squash</a> show their widest variety and dazzle us with their sweet flavors. Broccoli, cauliflower, and leafy greens benefit from a good frost. Chanterelle and porcini mushrooms poke up from a carpet of fallen leaves. </p><p><img alt="" xlink:actuate="onLoad" xlink:show="embed" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Pictures/Magazine%20Pictures/Magazine%20Fall%20Pictures/Autumn%20Dishes/Autumn%20Fruit%20Still%20Life.xml#data" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Pictures/Magazine%20Pictures/Magazine%20Fall%20Pictures/Autumn%20Dishes/Autumn%20Fruit%20Still%20Life"/></p><p><a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Desserts/Upside%20Down%20Apple%20Cake%20Article.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Editorial/Content/Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Desserts/Upside%20Down%20Apple%20Cake%20Article">Apples</a> from Washington and New York make for fresh cider drinking all over the chilling countryside while seasonal fruits like pomegranates and persimmons again become available after a long absence, forming the <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Navigation/Microsites/05_Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Desserts/Desserts%20Fall%20Page.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Navigation/Microsites/05_Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Desserts/Desserts%20Fall%20Page">perfect finish to an autumn meal.</a></p><p/><p class="p--heading-3">Complementing Your Meal</p><p>Autumn favorites of comforting rich stews and <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Videos/How-To/How%20to%20sear%20and%20roast%20meats%20Vimeo%20Video.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Videos/How-To/How%20to%20sear%20and%20roast%20meats%20Vimeo%20Video">tender braised meats</a>, such as this <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Main/Spicy%20Duck%20Recipe%20Article.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Editorial/Content/Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Main/Spicy%20Duck%20Recipe%20Article">delicious spicy duck,</a> paired with bold red wines are the perfect complement for chilly autumn nights. When menus change to rich sauces and piping-hot dishes, keep in mind complementing aromas, textures, and dominant flavors when choosing a wine for a <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Navigation/Microsites/05_Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Fall%20Recipes%20Page.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Navigation/Microsites/05_Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Fall%20Recipes%20Page">fall meal.</a> Pair the complex flavors of spiced stews and <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Videos/How-To/How%20to%20sear%20and%20roast%20meats%20Vimeo%20Video.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Videos/How-To/How%20to%20sear%20and%20roast%20meats%20Vimeo%20Video">braised meats</a> with a full-bodied cabernet sauvignon or velvety merlot, and accompany rich chocolate desserts in the colder months with a luscious pinot noir.</p><p><a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Main/Spicy%20Duck%20Recipe%20Article.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Editorial/Content/Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Main/Spicy%20Duck%20Recipe%20Article"><img alt="" xlink:actuate="onLoad" xlink:show="embed" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Pictures/Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Spicy%20Duck%20Picture.xml#data" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Pictures/Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Spicy%20Duck%20Picture"/><br/>Try our Spicy Duck Recipe</a></p><p class="p--heading-3">Soups and Stews</p><p>Nothing warms the soul like a <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Starters/Pumpkin%20Cream%20Soup%20Recipe%20Article.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Editorial/Content/Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Starters/Pumpkin%20Cream%20Soup%20Recipe%20Article">hot bowl of soup</a> or a comforting stew, slow-simmered on the stove.  <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Navigation/Microsites/05_Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Starters/Starters%20Fall%20Page.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Navigation/Microsites/05_Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Starters/Starters%20Fall%20Page">Soups and stews</a> can be among the simplest of creations, but their often complex flavor can belie <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Videos/How-To/How%20to%20make%20pureed%20vegetable%20soups%20Vimeo%20Video.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Videos/How-To/How%20to%20make%20pureed%20vegetable%20soups%20Vimeo%20Video">the ease of their creation.</a><br/></p><p><img alt="" xlink:actuate="onLoad" xlink:show="embed" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Pictures/Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Beans%20Soup%20Picture.xml#data" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Pictures/Recipes/Fall%20Recipes/Beans%20Soup%20Picture"/></p><p>Every <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Pots/Pots%20External%20Category%20Page.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Pots/Pots%20External%20Category%20Page">pot</a> is endlessly customizable — substitute an ingredient here, subtract one there, add a new one this time — so each <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Pots/Pots%20External%20Category%20Page.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Pots/Pots%20External%20Category%20Page">pot</a> takes on its maker's personality. Most soups and stews benefit from a slow simmer and gain in flavor if made a day ahead, which makes this cooking method a favorite of the Slow Food movement.</p><p class="p--heading-3">Casseroles</p><p>Even for the most organized cook, making a quick and wholesome dinner can be a challenge. Making <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Baking%20Pans/Baking%20Pans%20External%20Category%20Page.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Baking%20Pans/Baking%20Pans%20External%20Category%20Page">casseroles</a> is a simple, delicious way to pack a lot of goodness into one <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Baking%20Pans/Baking%20Pans%20External%20Category%20Page.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Baking%20Pans/Baking%20Pans%20External%20Category%20Page">pan</a>. With most having a short prep time and easy, unattended cooking, these "weeknight wonders" deliver a home-cooked, satisfying supper to the table in no time. <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Baking%20Pans/Baking%20Pans%20External%20Category%20Page.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Baking%20Pans/Baking%20Pans%20External%20Category%20Page">Casseroles</a> feature hearty yet familiar flavors everyone loves. Make a hearty <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Baking%20Pans/Baking%20Pans%20External%20Category%20Page.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Baking%20Pans/Baking%20Pans%20External%20Category%20Page">casserole</a> ahead of time to reheat for a quick and easy weeknight meal, or serve one as part of your Sunday dinner tradition with friends and family.</p><p><a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../Products/Fall%20Campaign/Glass%20Casserole%20Product%20Teaser.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Editorial/Products/Fall%20Campaign/Glass%20Casserole%20Product%20Teaser"><img alt="" xlink:actuate="onLoad" xlink:show="embed" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Pictures/Product%20Teaser%20Pictures/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Baking%20Pans/PC_GLASS_CASSEROLE%20Frontshot.xml#data" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Pictures/Product%20Teaser%20Pictures/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Baking%20Pans/PC_GLASS_CASSEROLE%20Frontshot"/></a></p><p><a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../Products/Fall%20Campaign/Glass%20Casserole%20Product%20Teaser.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Editorial/Products/Fall%20Campaign/Glass%20Casserole%20Product%20Teaser">This Pyrex casserole</a><a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../Products/Fall%20Campaign/Glass%20Casserole%20Product%20Teaser.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Editorial/Products/Fall%20Campaign/Glass%20Casserole%20Product%20Teaser"><span class="underline"> dish</span></a> goes from oven to table quite nicely.</p><p class="p--heading-3">Desserts</p><p>It's time to get cozy and get <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Appliances/Mixers/Mixers%20External%20Category%20Page.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Appliances/Mixers/Mixers%20External%20Category%20Page">baking</a>. With the cooler weather upon us, homemade desserts using fresh fall ingredients are the perfect finish to a savory meal — or just a sweet treat whenever you please. From puddings to cakes to pies, <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/04_Deli/To%20Eat/To%20Eat%20External%20Page.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/04_Deli/To%20Eat/To%20Eat%20External%20Page">luscious desserts</a> flavored with the fruits and nuts of fall and spiced with cinnamon, nutmeg, ginger, and other flavors are just right for a crisp autumn night.</p><p><img alt="" xlink:actuate="onLoad" xlink:show="embed" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Pictures/Magazine%20Pictures/Magazine%20Fall%20Pictures/Autumn%20Dishes/Cinnamon%20Rolls%20Picture.xml#data" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Pictures/Magazine%20Pictures/Magazine%20Fall%20Pictures/Autumn%20Dishes/Cinnamon%20Rolls%20Picture"/><br/></p><blockquote><p><strong>We like …</strong></p><p>Here are some items we like to help you make the most of your autumn dishes.</p><p><a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../Products/Fall%20Campaign/Red%20Enamel%20Pot%20Product%20Teaser.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Editorial/Products/Fall%20Campaign/Red%20Enamel%20Pot%20Product%20Teaser"><img alt="" xlink:actuate="onLoad" xlink:show="embed" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Pictures/Product%20Teaser%20Pictures/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Pots/PC_ENAMEL_POT%20Frontshot.xml#data" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Pictures/Product%20Teaser%20Pictures/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Pots/PC_ENAMEL_POT%20Frontshot"/></a><br/></p><p><a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../Products/Fall%20Campaign/Red%20Enamel%20Pot%20Product%20Teaser.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Editorial/Products/Fall%20Campaign/Red%20Enamel%20Pot%20Product%20Teaser">This red enamel pot</a> and its tight-fitting lid retains heat beautifully, and is great for cooking soups and stews.</p><p/><p><a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../Products/Fall%20Campaign/Knife%20Set%20Product%20Teaser.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Editorial/Products/Fall%20Campaign/Knife%20Set%20Product%20Teaser"><img alt="" xlink:actuate="onLoad" xlink:show="embed" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Pictures/Product%20Teaser%20Pictures/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Knives/PC_KNIFE_BLOCK%20Frontshot.xml#data" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Pictures/Product%20Teaser%20Pictures/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Knives/PC_KNIFE_BLOCK%20Frontshot"/></a><br/></p><p><a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../Products/Fall%20Campaign/Knife%20Set%20Product%20Teaser.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Editorial/Products/Fall%20Campaign/Knife%20Set%20Product%20Teaser">Knife Set</a> - Central to all your culinary creations, these <a xlink:show="replace" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="coremedia:///cap/resources/../../../../Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Knives/Knives%20External%20Category%20Page.xml" cmexport:path="/Sites/Aurora%20Augmentation/United%20States/English/Navigation/Fragments/Perfect%20Chef%20Categories/02_In%20The%20Kitchen/Knives/Knives%20External%20Category%20Page">knives</a> are durable, slick, and ready for your cutting needs. This complete set will prove indispensable.</p></blockquote></div></detailText>
